transArray.content: The decoration is decorated with modern literature and art, humanized design, and there are robots that deliver items, which is very cool. It has its own small yard for parking, which is convenient!

May time slow down, may old friends never be separated, with your company, Xiao Ji will never be alone! Thank you for staying here, friends. We will be with you wholeheartedly throughout the seasons! Looking forward to every stay with you~
